      #time_nudge.contents.headspace
        h1 Rainbow Timer
        button.toggle.spacing
          div.left.on
          div.right
        p The Rainbow Timer is a subtle rainbow that grows every five minutes you spend on one of your Nudge sites.
        p It helps you see when you‚Äôre getting sucked in, without disrupting you too much. You can still continue using the site while the Rainbow Timer grows.
        .p-highlight.spacing
          p üí° Tip: you can always hide the Rainbow Timer by hovering over the Nudge logo and selecting the second button from the bottom.
        #js-onboarding.full-width
          .horizontal.onboarding-bar.spacing.full-width
            button.primary#js-onboarding-enable Enable the Rainbow Timer
            button.secondary#js-onboarding-skip Skip this feature
          .horizontal.onboarding-bar.spacing.full-width(style="display:none")
            button.primary.pink#js-next Next: Hider
    .horizontal.centered.onboarding-preview
      .left
      .center
        img(src="../../img/preview/timenudger.png").preview-image
      .right


